flowchart LR
    Client([Client]) --> GW[API Gateway]
    GW --> Auth[Authorizer Function\nJWT / OAuth]
    Auth -->|Valid token| Router{Route Matcher}
    Auth -->|Invalid| Reject([401 Unauthorized])
    Router -->|POST /upload| FnUpload[Upload Handler\nFunction]
    Router -->|GET /data| FnQuery[Query Handler\nFunction]
    Router -->|POST /process| FnProcess[Process Handler\nFunction]
    FnUpload --> S3[(Object Storage)]
    FnQuery --> DB[(Managed Database)]
    FnProcess --> Queue[[Message Queue]]
    Queue --> FnWorker[Worker Function\nasync trigger]
    FnWorker --> DB
    FnWorker --> Notify[Notification Service\nSNS / SES]
    S3 -->|Storage event trigger| FnWorker
